layerGroup.name: GEOMORPH_FlindersReefs_BGU
layerGroup.title: Seabed geomorphology of the Flinders Reefs (Coral Sea) - multi-scale resolution
layerGroup.abstractTxt: Bathymetric high and low geomorphology of the Flinders Reefs (Coral Sea). This layer group comprises Basic Geomorphic Units (BGU) visualised across four levels of scale: broadscale, mediumscale, medium-finescale, and finescale. Layers are arranged hierarchically, with broadscale BGU serving as the background layer and finescale positioned as the top layer. Zoom-based styling progressively switches on more detailed layers as zoom level increases.
